beam, t and L are related,

00:46:11.300 --> 00:46:14.240
so this is now the
unitary transformation

00:46:14.240 --> 00:46:17.980
if you propagate
through that crystal.

00:46:24.820 --> 00:46:33.780
We are now defining
that by saying

00:46:33.780 --> 00:46:36.650
we have this non-linear
susceptibility,

00:46:36.650 --> 00:46:39.540
things will be proportional
