00:49:53.620 --> 00:49:56.540
You see that the operator
for the combined Hilbert

00:49:56.540 --> 00:49:59.350
space of the two photons
gives you a phase shift of pi.

00:49:59.350 --> 00:50:02.440
It's not pi for one photon
times pi for the other one--

00:50:02.440 --> 00:50:04.180
